: This species was revised, redescribed, and illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9F4B5DFF83E57053FE82C16774FA55" author="ASSING, V." box="[987,1151,1481,1505]" pageId="66" pageNumber="183" pagination="87 - 175" refId="ref57174" refString="ASSING, V. 2016 a: A revision of Zyras STEPHENS sensu strictu of China, Taiwan, and Hong Kong, with records and (re-) descriptions of some species from other regions (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae: Lomechusini). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde A, Neue Serie 9: 87 - 175." type="journal article" year="2016">ASSING (2016a</bibRefCitation>
